µC0Ghandy: What's your opinion about chances to become a successful computer platform in commercial aspects?

µC1Crisot: Eternal question ;) I don't want to answer you with "it is possible" or "it isn't". We need MANY, MANY, MANY work on the commercial part or technical part of the AmigaOne, to dream about a commercial future...

µC0Ghandy: That's right!


µC0Ghandy: What are your own future plans??

µC1Crisot: A next demo, but much more work on it, no buggs, 3D acceleration, etc... Just to prove what an AmigaOne is able to do ;)

µC0Ghandy: I wish you guys much luck with your projects!! And thanks a lot for the quick interview!!



